DISCLAIMER

This software is designed to convert websites into Android applications. Users
are responsible for:

1. Ensuring they have the legal right to create applications from the websites
   they convert.

2. Complying with all applicable laws and regulations regarding app distribution.

3. Respecting intellectual property rights of website owners and content creators.

4. Obtaining necessary permissions and licenses for commercial use.

5. Ensuring their use of the converted applications complies with Google Play
   Store policies and Android platform guidelines.

The authors and contributors of this software are not responsible for any misuse,
legal issues, or damages resulting from the use of this software.

