PRIVACY & DATA

This software:
- Does not collect or transmit user data to external servers
- Processes all builds locally on your server
- Does not include analytics or telemetry
- Stores temporary files only during build process

Users deploying this software are responsible for:
- Implementing their own privacy policies
- Complying with GDPR, CCPA, and other data protection regulations
- Securing their server and protecting user data
- Disclosing data collection practices to their users

